@@ -0,0 +1,199 @@
+/*
+ * Freescale Management Complex (MC) device passthrough using VFIO
+ *
+ * Copyright (C) 2013-2016 Freescale Semiconductor, Inc.
+ * Author: Bharat Bhushan <bharat.bhushan@nxp.com>
